<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Security Alert - New Login Detected</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 100%);">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 100%); padding: 40px 20px;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background: #1E293B; border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3); box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);">
          
          <tr>
            <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #EF4444 0%, #F59E0B 100%); padding: 50px 40px; text-align: center;">
              <div style="width: 90px; height: 90px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 20px; backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4); line-height: 90px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">
                <span style="font-size: 45px;">üîí</span>
              </div>
              <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);">New Login Detected</h1>
              <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); margin: 10px 0 0; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500;">Security notification</p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 50px 40px;">
              <p style="color: #F1F5F9; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600;">Hi <span style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #EF4444, #F59E0B); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;">{{name}}</span>,</p>

              <p style="color: #CBD5E1; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; margin: 0 0 35px;">
                We detected a new login to your {{appName}} account. If this was you, you can safely ignore this email. If you don't recognize this activity, please secure your account immediately.
              </p>

              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 100%); border: 2px solid #EF4444; border-radius: 16px; padding: 30px; margin-bottom: 35px;">
                <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin: 0 0 20px; font-weight: 700;">Login Details</p>
                <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);">
                      <span style="color: #64748B; font-size: 14px; display: block;">Date & Time</span>
                      <span style="color: #F1F5F9; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; display: block; margin-top: 5px;">{{formatDateTime loginDate}}</span>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  {{#if ipAddress}}
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);">
                      <span style="color: #64748B; font-size: 14px; display: block;">IP Address</span>
                      <span style="color: #EF4444; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; display: block; margin-top: 5px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;">{{ipAddress}}</span>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  {{/if}}
                  {{#if location}}
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);">
                      <span style="color: #64748B; font-size: 14px; display: block;">Location</span>
                      <span style="color: #F1F5F9; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; display: block; margin-top: 5px;">{{location}}</span>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  {{/if}}
                  {{#if device}}
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 12px 0;">
                      <span style="color: #64748B; font-size: 14px; display: block;">Device</span>
                      <span style="color: #F1F5F9; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; display: block; margin-top: 5px;">{{device}}</span>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  {{/if}}
                </table>
              </div>

              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15) 0%, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.05) 100%); border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; padding: 25px; margin-bottom: 35px; border-radius: 12px;">
                <p style="color: #FCD34D; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 10px; font-weight: 700;">
                  ‚ö†Ô∏è Don't Recognize This Login?
                </p>
                <p style="color: #FDE68A; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7;">
                  If this wasn't you, your account may be compromised. Please change your password immediately and review your account activity.
                </p>
              </div>

              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 35px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center">
                    <a href="{{secureAccountUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #EF4444 0%, #F59E0B 100%); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 18px 50px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.4); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin: 0 8px 10px;">
                      Secure My Account
                    </a>
                    {{#if reviewActivityUrl}}
                    <a href="{{reviewActivityUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; background: rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.8); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 18px 50px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin: 0 8px 10px;">
                      Review Activity
                    </a>
                    {{/if}}
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="color: #CBD5E1; font-size: 16px; margin: 40px 0 0;">
                Stay safe,<br>
                <strong style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #EF4444, #F59E0B); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;">The {{appName}} Security Team</strong>
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); padding: 30px 40px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);">
              <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 10px;">
                Need help? <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #EF4444; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">{{supportEmail}}</a>
              </p>
              <p style="color: #64748B; font-size: 12px; margin: 10px 0 0;">¬© {{currentYear}} {{appName}}. Your security is our priority.</p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>